settings.title: Do you have a refund or return policy?
settings.text:
We do often have the ability to change the shipping address on an order if the request comes in quickly. The typical requirement for us to be able to make any changes is within one hour of the order being placed. For insurance and liability requirements, we do need to get the new address approved by our third-party fraud protection service called Signifyd.

Please note that changing the shipping location after order placement will cause delays on your shipment. It is important that you let us know of an address change as soon as possible after your order is placed, as we cannot reroute a package once it has left our facility.

If the item has left one of our facilities, you can certainly give FedEx Customer Service a call and provide them with the tracking information to assist in having the package held at a nearby FedEx pickup location.
